name: CNN
text:
Amazon CEO Jeff Bezos is opening the doors of his first preschool, the Bezos Academy.

It's the first location of a network of tuition-free preschools serving children in underserved communities spearheaded by Bezos' philanthropic arm, Day One Fund. https://t.co/1PVVwL3YVZ

name: CNN
text: Plumber Judaline Cassidy is encouraging girls to follow in her footsteps through her "Tools and Tiaras" program. She runs camps, monthly workshops and mentoring programs that introduce girls to construction trades like plumbing, carpentry and electrical. https://t.co/NfIDRexlzK https://t.co/z51EOnWlIl
